 Squash←{
     ⍝ ⍺ ←→ Project Space
     ⍝ ⍵ ←→ Commit Message
     ⍺←0
     p←GetProjectSpace ⍺
     b←p GetCurrentBranch''
     b≡'master':'No squashing the master.'
     p IsDirty'':'Uncommitted changes.'
     m←⍵,(0=≢⍵)/'Save point'
     ca←↑#.Git.RunGitCommand'merge-base master ',b
     ⎕←⊃p RunGitCommand'reset --soft ',ca
     ⎕←⊃p RunGitCommand'commit -m "',m,'"'
     'Done'
 }
